    <MSection name='description'>
      <MList listtype='unordered'>
        <MListItem>
          <MParagraph>tmon = testmon() constructs a testing monitor. It can be used to monitor the running of testing functions, checking the assertions and capturing the exceptions, and making records.</MParagraph>
        </MListItem>
      </MList>
    </MSection>
    <MSection name='remarks'>
      <MList listtype='unordered'>
        <MListItem>
          <MParagraph>The monitor keeps the recorded information in a single linked list, in order to facilitate dynamic appending.</MParagraph>
